  "Masahiro Miki founded and owns the majority of discount shoe store chain ABC-Mart.",
  "The chain had earlier benefited from the influx of tourists into Japan, especially from China and Southeast Asia. ",
  "ABC-Mart own U.S. shoe brand LaCrosse, which owns the Danner brand of shoes. ",
